{"tid":1757963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【尋死線共識】12.08 民陣集會前 政府須實際回應五大訴求剩餘部份 否則或反對集會即全面行動升級","createTime":"2019-11-26T20:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T08:38:31.000Z","uid":150625,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e82b6d12238514452f0d41e7df92a8e862eaf089","tid":1757963,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T20:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtuwU3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtuwU3d.jpg&h=87ea8c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如題 時間絕對足夠甚至太多! 大家同唔同意? <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對集會即等同提早拒絕<br />\n立即升級<br />\n不作正面回應只講狗屁<br />\n12.09起全面升級</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n死線前大家全力文宣! 修補連儂牆! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同支持其他行動<br />\n［行動］［日程］2019年12月光復香港計劃<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757922</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJFkfDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJFkfDY.jpg&h=9d6a0942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SUkZ5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SUkZ5H.jpg&h=552f9641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發！！！廣告界正式宣佈罷工！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755050</a><br />\n五大訴求未完架！響應廣告界，下星期搞一次全民大罷工！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755460</a><br />\n<br />\n升級既話<br />\n工作日黎明行動、大三罷承接上述行動無限期發動!<br />\n前線手足閃電開花、突發機場默默進行!<br />\n總之兄弟爬山各有各做!"},{"pid":"8c4598ed47fe360ad4ed30d1af186a2fbb78c209","tid":1757963,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T20:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWADBXZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/